# {{lb|en|primitive Church}} A person who first brought the gospel to a city or region.
# {{lb|en|Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints}} A [[patriarch]].
# {{lb|en|by extension}} A person marked by [[extreme]] enthusiasm for or support of any [[cause]], particularly with regard to religion.
